import { Box, Button, TextField, Typography } from '@mui/material'
import React from 'react'


const Auth = () => {
  return (
    <>
      <form>
        <Box display='flex' flexDirection='column' justifyContent='center' alignItems='center' boxShadow= "10px 10px 20px #ccc" padding={3} borderRadius={5} marginTop={5} margin="auto">
          <Typography variant='h4'>Login</Typography>
          <TextField />
          <TextField />
          <TextField />
          <Button>Submit</Button>
          <Button>Change to Signup</Button>
        </Box>
      </form>
    </>
  )
}

export default Auth
